  questions:
  - question: "Deprem s\u0131ras\u0131nda mutfakta en b\xFCy\xFCk tehlikelerden biri
      nedir?"
    answers:
    - "Masa \xF6rt\xFCs\xFC"
    - "A\xE7\u0131k dolap ve k\u0131r\u0131labilir e\u015Fyalar"
    - "Buzdolab\u0131 sesi"
