  - question: "Deprem s\u0131ras\u0131nda ocak a\xE7\u0131ksa ne yap\u0131lmal\u0131?"
    answers:
    - "Pani\u011Fe kap\u0131lmak"
    - "Deprem bitince g\xFCvenli \u015Fekilde kontrol etmek"
    - "Hemen ate\u015Fe su d\xF6kmek"
    - "Cam a\xE7mak i\xE7in ko\u015Fmak"
